TurboFly is a fast futuristic racing game on the spacecraft from the company Osaris Software. This game is the full version, which includes:
- 3 game modes (Normal, a race and endurance race)
- 5 types of space ships with different weapons
- 23 tracks with beautiful 3D landscapes (Moscow, St. Petersburg, Kazan, Sochi, Arkhangelsk, etc.)
- Table Online Records
Enjoy races in spaceships!
